Analyze the Jira issue thoroughly — read the title, description, scope, and
acceptance criteria. Proceed only if you genuinely believe changes are
required in **this** repository.

Check the Jira issue description for phrases like:
- "No {{ repo_label }} changes required"
- "Out of Scope: {{ repo_label }} changes"
